{"tid":1563064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實消防一定知內情，但係佢地唔能夠企出黎直接指證","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T09:26:19.000Z","uid":321231,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e87f805e0d16585ccefcaddb0ec67e9f940e1831","tid":1563064,"uid":321231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"其實消防一定知內情，但係佢地唔能夠企出黎直接指證。<br />\n -&gt; 因為佢地無'證物'，唯一證物就係黨鐵 CCTV。<br />\n除非當時人拍片，但咁多狗你偷拍，自身都有危險。<br />\n<br />\n記者會報過既fact： <br />\n1. 狗有&quot;移動&quot;過傷者。<br />\n2. 消防見到既所有傷者，都係安全送左院。<br />\n3. 消防有篤左警察唔比佢地入站，警察多次講大話下邊月台無傷者。<br />\n<br />\n重大疑點： 有人唔見左，而消防比到既解釋，就係&quot;點錯數&quot;。 而佢地回應唔到，可唔可以係有警察令到有傷者 &quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被消失</span></strong></span>&quot;？<br />\n <br />\n當有記者問，除左點錯數，會唔會有可能有警察移動左某傷者去左D無人見到既地方？;  消防答案係：我地只可以講我地當時「見到d 咩野」，有機會係我地數錯左。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">消防依家已經做哂助攻比我地，我地同傳媒要做既，就係同黨鐵追究CCTV （證物）</span></span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有錯請補充。"},{"pid":"ccf34af23df92d719021c22e909f616704c4009c","tid":1563064,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ 